家庭启蒙口语大全 · 中英对照 + 口语化补充版
一、晨间 routine
1. 叫醒/起床气
0–2岁：早上好宝贝，该起床啦。Good morning, sweetie! Time to wake up.
💬 Wakey wakey! / Morning, baby.

2–3岁：起床啦！睡得好吗？Rise and shine! Did you sleep well?
💬 Up you go! / Sleep good?

3–5岁：已经是早上了，我们看看今天天气怎么样。It’s morning already. Let’s see what the weather is like today.
💬 Time to get up, sleepyhead. / Look outside—sunny or rainy?

2. 穿衣服
0–2岁：我们穿上蓝色衬衫，胳膊举起来。Let’s put on your blue shirt. Arms up!
💬 Shirt on. Arms up! / Blue shirt today?

2–3岁：今天想穿哪件？红的还是蓝的？Which shirt do you want to wear today, the red one or the blue one?
💬 Red or blue? You pick.

3–5岁：你能试着自己穿袜子吗？Can you try to put on your socks by yourself?
💬 Try your socks. You can do it.

3. 刷牙洗脸
0–2岁：张大嘴，刷牙啦。Open wide! Brush your teeth.
💬 Aahhh... brush brush!

2–3岁：挤一点牙膏在牙刷上。Squeeze a little toothpaste on your brush.
💬 Just a little toothpaste, okay?

3–5岁：我们要刷两分钟，我设个闹钟。We need to brush for two minutes. I’ll set a timer.
💬 Two minutes—let's go!

4. 梳头发
0–2岁：我们梳梳头，轻轻的。Let’s brush your hair. Nice and gentle.
💬 Brush brush. Nice and easy.

2–3岁：今天想扎马尾还是编辫子？Do you want a ponytail or a braid today?
💬 Ponytail or braid?

3–5岁：别动，马上就好，你真好看。Hold still, I’m almost done. You look great!
💬 Almost done. Pretty girl / Handsome boy!

5. 吃早餐
0–2岁：麦片真好吃，还要吗？Yummy cereal. Want more?
💬 Good? More?

2–3岁：早餐想吃什么？牛奶还是酸奶？What would you like for breakfast? Milk or yogurt?
💬 Milk or yogurt? Pick one.

3–5岁：吃饭时要好好坐在桌边。Please sit nicely at the table while you eat.
💬 Stay in your chair, please.

二、如厕与自理
1. 表达尿意/便意
0–2岁：要尿尿吗？Do you need to go potty?
💬 Potty? / Gotta go?

2–3岁：想尿尿的时候告诉我。Tell me when you need to pee, okay?
💬 Tell Mama when you need to pee.

3–5岁：出门前记得上厕所。Remember to go potty before we leave the house.
💬 Potty first, then we go.

2. 擦屁股/洗手
0–2岁：洗洗手，搓一搓。Let’s wash your hands. Rub rub rub!
💬 Wash hands. Rub rub!

2–3岁：用肥皂，好好冲干净。Use soap and rinse well.
💬 Soap first. Rinse off.

3–5岁：别忘了关水龙头，把手擦干。Don’t forget to turn off the tap and dry your hands.
💬 Turn off the water. Wipe your hands.

3. 如厕训练
0–2岁：我们在小马桶上坐一会儿。Let’s sit on the potty for a little bit.
💬 Sit on the potty. Try?

2–3岁：你做到了！尿到马桶里啦！You did it! You peed in the potty!
💬 You did it! Pee in the potty!

3–5岁：现在可以穿大孩子的内裤了。Now we can wear big-kid underwear.
💬 Big-kid undies now!

4. 擤鼻涕/剪指甲
0–2岁：妈妈帮你擦擦鼻涕。Let me wipe your nose.
💬 Wipe your nose.

2–3岁：像这样擤鼻涕，哼！Blow your nose like this – honk!
💬 Blow—honk! Like this.

3–5岁：指甲长了，剪一下免得抓伤。Your nails are long. Let’s cut them so they don’t scratch.
💬 Nails are long. Clip clip!

三、室内活动
客厅/游戏区
玩积木/乐高
0–2岁：把积木叠起来，高，高，高！Stack the blocks. Up, up, up!
💬 Up, up! More blocks.

2–3岁：能找到红色的积木吗？放最上面。Can you find the red block? Put it on top.
💬 Where's the red one? On top.

3–5岁：我们一起搭城堡，我来搭塔，你来搭围墙。Let’s build a castle together. I’ll make the tower, you make the wall.
💬 Let's make a castle. You do the wall, I'll do the tower.

拼图/桌游
0–2岁：这块放哪里？试试这儿。Where does this piece go? Try here.
💬 Try here? Does it fit?

2–3岁：轮到你了，我等着。It’s your turn. I’ll wait.
💬 Your turn. Go ahead.

3–5岁：真棒！你自己拼好了拼图。Good job! You finished the puzzle all by yourself.
💬 You did it! All by yourself!

过家家
0–2岁：宝宝睡着了，嘘……Baby is sleeping. Shhh…
💬 Shhh... baby sleeping.

2–3岁：我给你煮汤，你喜欢吗？I’ll cook some soup for you. Do you like it?
💬 Here's some soup. Yummy?

3–5岁：你当爸爸，我当宝宝，今天我们做什么？You be the daddy, I’ll be the baby. What should we do today?
💬 I'm the baby, you're the daddy. Now what?

看电视/ipad
0–2岁：我们看一集小猪佩奇。Let’s watch one episode of Peppa Pig.
💬 One Peppa, then off.

2–3岁：再看五分钟，然后关掉。Five more minutes, then we turn it off.
💬 Five minutes, then bye-bye TV.

3–5岁：从节目里学到了什么？What did you learn from that show?
💬 What did you see? Tell me.

收拾玩具
0–2岁：该收拾了！把球放盒子里。Time to clean up! Put the ball in the box.
💬 Clean up time! Ball in the box.

2–3岁：你能把所有积木放回箱子里吗？Can you put all the blocks back in the bin?
💬 Blocks away. In the bin.

3–5岁：我们来分类玩具：车放这儿，娃娃放那儿。Let’s sort the toys: cars here, dolls there.
💬 Cars here, dolls there. Let's sort.

阅读/学习角
选书/翻书
0–2岁：看这本书！有小狗。Look at this book! It has a doggy.
💬 Look—doggy!

2–3岁：你想让我读哪本书？Which book do you want me to read?
💬 Pick a book.

3–5岁：你能告诉我这页发生了什么吗？Can you tell me what’s happening on this page?
💬 What's going on here?

指读/提问
0–2岁：那是什么？是小猫。What’s that? It’s a cat.
💬 What's that? Cat!

2–3岁：猫在哪里？能指给我看吗？Where is the cat? Can you point to it?
💬 Where's the cat? Point!

3–5岁：猫是什么颜色的？它怎么叫？What color is the cat? And what sound does it make?
💬 What color? Meow?

画画/手工
0–2岁：我们用蜡笔画画。Let’s scribble with the crayon.
💬 Scribble scribble!

2–3岁：画个圆，不错哟！Draw a circle. Good try!
💬 Make a circle. Good job!

3–5岁：我们给奶奶做张卡片，你可以画些花。Let’s make a card for Grandma. You can draw some flowers.
💬 Let's make Grandma a card. Draw flowers?

四、厨房与用餐
参与做饭
0–2岁：帮我搅拌一下碗。Help me stir the bowl.
💬 Stir, stir!

2–3岁：你能洗一下西红柿吗？小心点。Can you wash the tomato? Be careful.
💬 Wash the tomato. Careful.

3–5岁：我们打个鸡蛋到碗里，轻轻敲。Let’s crack an egg into the bowl. Tap it gently.
💬 Crack the egg. Tap tap—good!

摆碗筷
0–2岁：把勺子放桌上。Put the spoon on the table.
💬 Spoon on the table.

2–3岁：你能给大家分盘子吗？Can you set the plates for everyone?
💬 Plates out, please.

3–5岁：我们需要三把叉子三把勺子，跟我一起数。We need three forks and three spoons. Count with me.
💬 Three forks, three spoons. Count with me.

用餐中
0–2岁：好吃吗？再吃点。Yummy? Eat some more.
💬 Good? More?

2–3岁：慢慢嚼。Chew your food slowly.
💬 Chew, chew. Slowly.

3–5岁：用叉子，别用手。Use your fork, not your fingers.
💬 Fork, not fingers.

收拾餐桌
0–2岁：盘子放这儿。Put your plate here.
💬 Plate here.

2–3岁：帮我擦擦桌子。Help me wipe the table.
💬 Wipe the table with me.

3–5岁：你能把碗端到水池吗？Can you carry your bowl to the sink?
💬 Take your bowl to the sink.

五、情绪与社交
表达情绪
0–2岁：你开心！你在笑呢。You’re happy! You’re smiling.
💬 You're happy! Big smile!

2–3岁：我看你难过了，要抱抱吗？I can see you’re sad. Do you want a hug?
💬 You look sad. Hug?

3–5岁：生气可以，但不能打人。我们聊聊吧。It’s okay to feel angry, but we don’t hit. Let’s talk about it.
💬 Angry is okay. No hitting. Tell me why.

情绪管理
0–2岁：嘘，没事，妈妈在。Shh, it’s okay. Mommy’s here.
💬 It's okay. Mama's here.

2–3岁：深呼吸，吸气，呼气。Take a deep breath. Breathe in, breathe out.
💬 Deep breath. In... out...

3–5岁：等你冷静下来我们再聊，我等着。When you’re calm, we can talk. I’ll wait.
💬 Calm down first. Then we talk.

社交礼仪
0–2岁：跟奶奶说拜拜。Say bye-bye to Grandma.
💬 Bye-bye, Grandma!

2–3岁：该说什么？谢谢！What do you say? Thank you!
💬 Say thank you.

3–5岁：能把玩具分享给朋友吗？Can you share your toy with your friend?
💬 Share with your friend?

六、亲子冲突与规则
不听话时
0–2岁：不行，别摸，烫。No, don’t touch. It’s hot.
💬 No touch. Hot!

2–3岁：你要听话，请把玩具捡起来。I need you to listen. Please pick up the toy.
💬 Listen. Pick up the toy, please.

3–5岁：如果再扔玩具，我就收走了。If you throw the toy again, I’ll have to take it away.
💬 Throw again, I take it away.

提要求被拒后
0–2岁：我知道你想要，但那个不安全。I know you want it, but it’s not safe.
💬 I know. Not safe.

2–3岁：我们今天不买，也许下次吧。We can’t buy it today. Maybe next time.
💬 Not today. Next time.

3–5岁：我知道你失望，我们找别的乐子吧。I understand you’re disappointed. Let’s find something else fun.
💬 I know you're sad. Let's find something else.

七、午睡/夜晚
睡前准备
0–2岁：午睡时间到，穿上睡衣吧。Time for nap. Let’s put on your pajamas.
💬 Nap time. Jammies on.

2–3岁：挑一本睡前故事书。Pick a book for bedtime.
💬 Pick a book.

3–5岁：跟爸爸说晚安，然后去刷牙。Let’s say goodnight to Daddy and brush your teeth.
💬 Say night-night to Daddy. Then brush.

哄睡
0–2岁：摇篮曲，宝宝，闭上眼睛。Rock-a-bye baby, close your eyes.
💬 Close your eyes. Rock rock.

2–3岁：躺下，我给你唱首歌。Lie down, I’ll sing you a song.
💬 Lie down. I'll sing.

3–5岁：今天你最喜欢什么？跟我说说。What was your favorite thing today? Tell me about it.
💬 What was fun today? Tell me.

夜醒/噩梦
0–2岁：嘘，没事，妈妈在，接着睡吧。Shh, it’s okay. Mommy’s here. Go back to sleep.
💬 It's okay. Mama's here. Go sleep.

2–3岁：做噩梦了吗？我在这儿呢。Did you have a bad dream? I’m right here.
💬 Bad dream? I'm here.

3–5岁：我们打开小夜灯，看，一切都好。Let’s turn on the nightlight. See, everything is fine.
💬 Light on. See? All good.

八、洗澡与身体护理
放水/试水温
0–2岁：进澡盆啦，水是温的。Let’s get in the tub. The water is warm.
💬 In the tub. Warm water.

2–3岁：试试水温，太热还是太冷？Can you feel the water? Is it too hot or too cold?
💬 Feel the water. Hot? Cold?

3–5岁：我加一点泡泡，看，泡泡！I’m adding some bubbles. Look, bubbles!
💬 Bubbles! Look!

洗头
0–2岁：头往后仰，我把泡泡冲掉。Tip your head back. I’ll rinse the soap out.
💬 Head back. Rinse now.

2–3岁：闭紧眼睛，水来了。Close your eyes tight, here comes the water.
💬 Eyes closed. Water coming!

3–5岁：你要是不想水进眼睛，就用毛巾挡着。You can hold this towel over your eyes if you want.
💬 Towel over your eyes? No water in eyes.

玩水
0–2岁：拍水，拍水，水里真好玩。Splash, splash! Fun in the water.
💬 Splash splash! Fun!

2–3岁：我们玩小黄鸭，嘎嘎。Let’s play with your rubber duck. Quack quack.
💬 Where's the duck? Quack quack!

3–5岁：你能把水倒进这个杯子里吗？Can you pour water into this cup?
💬 Pour water in the cup. Try?

九、外出场景
出门前
0–2岁：穿上鞋子。Let’s put on your shoes.
💬 Shoes on.

2–3岁：我们要去公园了，带帽子了吗？We’re going to the park. Do you have your hat?
💬 Park time! Hat on?

3–5岁：检查一下包：水杯、零食、玩具。Check your bag: water bottle, snacks, and your toy.
💬 Got your water? Snacks? Toy? Let's go.

在路上
0–2岁：看，大卡车！Look, a big truck!
💬 Big truck! Look!

2–3岁：等绿灯，红灯停。Let’s wait for the green light. Red means stop.
💬 Wait for green. Red says stop.

3–5岁：我们马上左转，拉好我的手。We’re going to turn left soon. Hold my hand.
💬 Turning left. Hold my hand.

超市
0–2岁：能把苹果放购物车里吗？Can you put the apple in the cart?
💬 Apple in the cart.

2–3岁：我们要买牛奶，你能找到吗？We need to buy milk. Can you find it?
💬 Where's the milk? Find it?

3–5岁：我们清单上有五样东西，来一样一样划掉。We have five things on our list. Let’s check them off.
💬 Five things on the list. Let's check.

游乐场
0–2岁：呜——滑下来啦。Whee! Down the slide.
💬 Whee! Slide!

2–3岁：排队等秋千。Wait your turn for the swing.
💬 Your turn soon. Wait.

3–5岁：我们去玩跷跷板，用腿蹬。Let’s go on the seesaw. Push with your legs.
💬 Seesaw! Push with your feet.

十、健康与安全
生病不舒服
0–2岁：你有点热，我们量一下体温。You feel warm. Let’s check your temperature.
💬 You're warm. Let's check.

2–3岁：哪里疼？指给我看。Where does it hurt? Show me.
💬 Where hurts? Show Mama.

3–5岁：你得吃点药才会好，药有点甜。You need to take some medicine so you’ll feel better. It tastes a little sweet.
💬 Time for medicine. It's a little sweet.

看医生/打针
0–2岁：医生很好，她只是听听你的心跳。The doctor is nice. She just wants to listen to your heart.
💬 Doctor's nice. Just listen to your heart.

2–3岁：很快就像蚊子叮一下。It’ll be a quick pinch, like a mosquito bite.
💬 Quick pinch—like a mosquito.

3–5岁：你真勇敢！打完针我们可以拿个贴纸。You’re so brave! After the shot, we can get a sticker.
💬 So brave! Shot done—sticker time!

安全提醒
0–2岁：别碰炉子，烫！Don’t touch the stove. Hot!
💬 No touch. Hot!

2–3岁：停车场里要靠近我。Stay close to me in the parking lot.
💬 Stay near me. Cars.

3–5岁：如果有陌生人给你糖，说不，然后来找我。If a stranger offers you candy, say no and come find me.
💬 Stranger gives candy? Say no. Find me.

十一、特殊时刻与节日
生日
0–2岁：生日快乐！看蛋糕！Happy birthday! Look at the cake!
💬 Happy birthday! Cake!

2–3岁：许个愿，吹蜡烛。Make a wish and blow out the candles.
💬 Make a wish. Blow!

3–5岁：拆礼物啦！猜猜里面是什么。Open your present! I wonder what’s inside.
💬 Open it! What's inside?

节日（春节/圣诞）
0–2岁：看，圣诞树！漂亮的灯。Look, a Christmas tree! Pretty lights.
💬 Christmas tree! Pretty lights.

2–3岁：如果你乖乖的，圣诞老人今晚就会来。Santa will come tonight if you’re good.
💬 Santa comes if you're good.

3–5岁：过年我们一起来包饺子。Let’s make dumplings together for Chinese New Year.
💬 Let's make dumplings!

十二、语言启蒙专属
指物命名
0–2岁：那是什么？球。What’s that? A ball.
💬 What's that? Ball!

2–3岁：你能指出狗在哪里吗？Can you point to the dog?
💬 Where's the dog? Point.

3–5岁：这是瓢虫，它有几个点？This is a ladybug. How many spots does it have?
💬 Ladybug! Count the spots.

简单问答
0–2岁：你的鼻子呢？在这儿！Where’s your nose? Here it is!
💬 Where's your nose? There it is!

2–3岁：这是什么颜色？红色。What color is this? It’s red.
💬 What color? Red!

3–5岁：这张图里发生了什么？男孩在跑步。What’s happening in this picture? The boy is running.
💬 What's he doing? Running!

日常描述
0–2岁：妈妈在做饭，好香。Mommy is cooking. Yummy smell.
💬 Mommy cooking. Smells good.

2–3岁：外面下雨了，我们来听雨声。It’s raining outside. Let’s listen to the rain.
💬 Rain rain. Listen.

3–5岁：爸爸快回来了，我们在门口等。Daddy is coming home soon. Let’s wait by the door.
💬 Daddy's almost home. Wait at the door.